First post and I already feel zeronet 8chan has been faster than real 8chan. We could stay here if there's nothing wrong with it.
However, can't zeronet use the DHT? it's supposed to solve all this tracker shit issues, which it does.

I intended to have a clearsign message in this post but it gets butchered and is unverifiable. So I'm linking a clearnet website.
https://0x0.st/zOx3.asc

Running a bajillion trackers is a really bad idea, don't do that. We all have the same default set of trackers, we don't need more unless they all go down.
